<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Put shallots, thyme, garlic, vegetable stock in a pan, season and bring to the boil and simmer until the shallots are tender, about 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Remove the shallots and garlic with a slotted spoon, add the swede, carrots and simmer until they are tender]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the chickpeas, shallots and garlic and continue simmering for for 5m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[If you wish to thicken the liquid slightly, liquidise a small ladleful and add back to the casserole. Season, add the parsley and serve.]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
